.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, plum, pumpkin, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, horror, martial-arts, satire
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, hip-hop, rock, techno
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, march, april
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person watching satire movies##3
 3. the fan of blues is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
 4. the fan of techno is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in april##5
 5. the person eating plum is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is between the fan of techno and the fan of rock##2
 7. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is in an even position##4
10. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
12. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere to the left of the person eating pumpkin##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | radish    | pumpkin      | plum   | apricot |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | martial-arts | horror | satire  |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop   | rock         | blues  | techno  |
| Birthday           | march      | september          | april | january  |

